{"tid":541181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查女人讓男人心動的瞬間,綁馬尾奪冠","createTime":"2018-01-26T07:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T09:50:21.000Z","uid":25345,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8d096a61e92428a3e68281d83aebf373e08190","tid":541181,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"[IMG][<a href=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/img/11620307/800-417.jpeg[/IMG]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimg%2F11620307%2F800-417.jpeg%5B%2FIMG%5D&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1ec222d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.twgreatdaily.com/img/11620307/800-417.jpeg[/IMG]</a><br />\n<br />\n很多男生都是馬尾控，更是因為男生很喜歡看女生嘴咬發圈，整理頭發準備要紮起頭發那一瞬間，頭發往後撥會露出脖子和臉，很容易讓男人臉紅心跳阿！<br />\n<br />\n特別對這個動作受不了的男人，欣賞認真、獨立的女孩，他們常會被女孩投入事情的神情給深深迷住。而綁馬尾時也會露出女人性感的後頸，當女生輕摸自己後頸時，他們巴不得對方的手是自己的，這種男人也有多愁善感、優柔寡斷的特質。"},{"pid":"6231d185cb348fbeaf642273e916724116fe6136","tid":541181,"uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/img/11620307/800-417.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimg%2F11620307%2F800-417.jpeg&h=c42bb7b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c47ab07ba49ad554e28e94ac08c8f57804c1dea8","tid":541181,"uid":39800,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"6231d185cb348fbeaf642273e916724116fe6136","tid":541181,"uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/img/11620307/800-417.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimg%2F11620307%2F800-417.jpeg&h=c42bb7b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"心動的原因已經唔關綁馬尾事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc5ba007f260009ef01b5110288813d01046863","tid":541181,"